                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Moffat</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.:]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bluefields</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-08-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 20, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Moffat reports that the Madriz forces under Gen. Rivas, numbering 700,
                    attacked and were defeated by Mena at Granada; that the attack resulted in
                    complete rout; and that Rivas was killed. Adds that the revolutionaries intend
                    immediate advance upon Masaya.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
